A new game lets you play Pac-Man, Pong, Space Invaders, and Donkey Kong all at once
If you're over 30, you probably have fond memories of "Pac-Man," "Donkey Kong," and "Space Invaders." You might have fond memories of "Pong," too. What if you could play all four games simultaneously? A new game called Pacapong lets you do just that. Sort of:   
